sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant G as Gateway
    participant S as State/Memory
    participant A as Agent (LLM)
    participant T as Tools (API)

    U->>G: "Рим на 3 дня, 800 EUR"
    G->>S: Init thread_id, state
    G->>A: Extract params
    A-->>S: Save {dest: Rome, days: 3, budget: 800}
    A->>T: search_flights(Rome, dates)
    T-->>A: JSON (top 3 flights)
    A-->>S: Update state (budget left: 500)
    A->>T: search_hotels(Rome, dates)
    T-->>A: JSON (top 3 hotels)
    A-->>S: Update state (budget left: 200)
    A->>A: Generate Markdown Itinerary
    A->>G: Result
    G->>U: Final Travel Plan
